{"tid":2298021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府指付錢為陳同佳請律師指稱全屬虛構　保留追究權利","createTime":"2020-11-23T17:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:28:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"cb96b8c36a0cb1cb093af00bf48330b84199fa04","tid":2298021,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"政府發表聲明，表示有關特區政府付錢為陳同佳聘請律師的指稱，全屬虛構，絕無其事；特區政府對捏造和散播虛假信息的人，予以強烈譴責，並保留法律追究的權利。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，政府希望陳同佳能夠早日赴台，接受法律制裁的立場一直沒有改變，希望台方以認真和務實的態度，不作任何政治操作，盡快接受陳同佳到台灣投案，以彰顯公義。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說，只要台灣履行應有的責任和司法公義，准許陳同佳入境，特區政府十分樂意作出合法可行的配合和安排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561520-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561520-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=da66d76c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561520-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=42adaa49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561520-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4f4f6e2ca236a4152cd0057009e9f013cd364268","tid":2298021,"uid":70786,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"百幾萬律師費唔通陳同佳自己變出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1108ac453351f04bd8432a978f4f7532910d5669","tid":2298021,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"人都x左啦<br />\n<br />\n仲洗咩揾律師"},{"pid":"86dfd13acedb6f52db36d6d1399645ba8703d5aa","tid":2298021,"uid":121197,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"台灣：OK咁我判打靶<br />\n港共你送唔送佳佳過嚟"},{"pid":"d126edbde8f799dc9a81191a18e304ddc281ed15","tid":2298021,"uid":49359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T00:33:00.000Z